<h3>Our Company</h3>
<p>
    Lavax, Inc. is an Illinois-based research, development, manufacturer and distributor of all-natural,
    environmentally-friendly personal health care products. We are a small, family-owned company, established
    nearly 14 years ago in Palatine, IL. Our goal is to utilize cutting edge science and technology to develop
    innovative health care products to improve human lives. To date, our research projects have won two Small
    Business Innovation Research grants from National Institutes of Health and two Grand Challenge Exploration
    grants from Bill & Melinda Gates Foundation.

<p>
    Every one of our all-natural product formulae was developed by a physician or laboratory researcher.
    All the formulae have been thoroughly tested and found to deliver immediate and powerful results,
    time after time. And they each are sold with a 100% money back guarantee.

